title: Huge tree blocks main road in Suffolk
text:
The tree has completely blocked the A1088 at Ixworth Thorpe Credit: St Edmundsbury Police A huge tree has come down across the A1088 in Suffolk at Ixworth Thorpe.
Police tweeted this picture of it asking Suffolk Highways to make it a priority.
The tree is completely blocking the road.
